data.description: Welcome home to 125 Derby Drive located in the Sought After Summerfield Development in Elverson!  This Adorable 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Townhome has been well maintained and Features a One Car Garage and a Full Basement. The Entire First Floor Boasts Beautiful Oak Hardwood Floors Throughout! Sunny Living Room has a French Door leading to the Back Deck & Overlooks a Horse Pasture. Eat in Kitchen has a Double Sink, Bay Window overlooking the Back Yard & Pendant Lighting Above. Kitchen also includes LG 5 Burner Electric Stove & Double Oven, Refrigerator & Dishwasher. Dining Room is Perfect for getting together with Family & Friends! 1st Floor Powder Room. Second Floor is Carpeted and has 3 Bedrooms all with Lighted Ceiling Fans & Large Closets. Main Bedroom has 16' Ceilings! Two Full Bathrooms round out the 2nd Floor. The Unfinished Daylight Basement includes the Washer & Dryer & High Ceilings for Finishing. One Car Garage w/ Opener.  Public Records is incorrect on # of Bathrooms and Interior Square Footage - Above Ground Finished Space is 1,543 s.f. Unfinished Basement is 751 s.f.  See attached Floor Plan. Schedule an appointment to see your future home today!
